OL,3,CParents of girl who died in kitchen
OL,4,Cincident serving 'life sentences',
OL,5,Cjury told
OL,7,FThe parents of a 14-year-old girl who
OL,8,Fdied after suffering a fatal wound to
OL,9,Fthe heart in their kitchen are serving
OL,10,F"life sentences", jurors who are
OL,11,Ftrying her father for murder were told.
OL,13,FSimon Vickers, 50, denies the murder
OL,14,Fand manslaughter of Scarlett Vickers
OL,15,Fat their home in Geneva Road,
OL,16,FDarlington, County Durham, last July.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@PO]
