OL,3,CParents of girl who died in kitchen
OL,4,Cincident serving 'life sentences',
OL,5,Cjury told
OL,7,FIn his closing speech to the jury,
OL,8,FNicholas Lumley KC, defending Vickers,
OL,9,Fsaid the prosecution did not have to
OL,10,Fadvance a motive, but there was not
OL,11,Fone.
OL,13,FThe experienced barrister described it
OL,14,Fas one of the "saddest and most
OL,15,Fserious cases".
OL,17,FHe reminded the jury how Scarlett's
OL,18,Fmother referred to the close family
OL,19,Fgroup as the "three S's".
