OL,3,CParents of girl who died in kitchen
OL,4,Cincident serving 'life sentences',
OL,5,Cjury told
OL,7,FMr Lumley said of the teenager: "She
OL,8,Fwas finding her independence,
OL,9,Fsupported at every turn by her father
OL,10,Fand her mother, there's no hint of
OL,11,Fdisharmony in that house."
OL,13,FHe added: "Neither parent asks for
OL,14,Fyour pity, your indulgence or even for
OL,15,Fyour forgiveness.
OL,17,F"Both parents are serving life
OL,18,Fsentences in the sense that their
OL,19,Flives are broken, their hearts are
OL,20,Fbroken and this process will not mend
OL,21,Fthem."
