OL,3,CParents of girl who died in kitchen
OL,4,Cincident serving 'life sentences',
OL,5,Cjury told
OL,7,FMr Lumley said: "You must decide
OL,8,Fwhether the loss of their daughter's
OL,9,Flife makes him a murderer.
OL,11,F"You must decide whether the loss of
OL,12,Ftheir daughter's life makes him guilty
OL,13,Fof manslaughter.
OL,15,F"Both require him to have deliberately
OL,16,Farmed himself and to have attacked his
OL,17,Fdaughter."
