OL,3,CParents of girl who died in kitchen
OL,4,Cincident serving 'life sentences',
OL,5,Cjury told
OL,7,FMark McKone KC, prosecuting, said that
OL,8,FVickers loved his daughter and he was
OL,9,F"devastated" by her death and he said
OL,10,Fthe jury would have sympathy for the
OL,11,Ffamily.
OL,13,FHe said that Vickers had lied about
OL,14,Fwhat happened that night.
OL,16,F"The prosecution submit that Mr
OL,17,FVickers did not and could not have
OL,18,Fstabbed his daughter through the heart
OL,19,Faccidentally," Mr McKone said.
