OL,7,FVickers could not have accidentally
OL,8,Fswiped the knife along the work
OL,9,Fsurface into her chest, the
OL,10,Fprosecution has said.
OL,12,FMr McKone reminded the jury Vickers
OL,13,Fhad smoked cannabis on the day and had
OL,14,Fbeen drinking wine.
