OL,3,CParents of girl who died in kitchen
OL,4,Cincident serving 'life sentences',
OL,5,Cjury told
OL,7,FAlcohol coupled with an incident where
OL,8,Fhis daughter and his partner threw
OL,9,Fgrapes at each other in the kitchen,
OL,10,Fwith some ending on the floor where
OL,11,Ftheir dog could eat them, could have
OL,12,Fled him to become irritated, the
OL,13,Fprosecution said.
OL,15,FThe prosecution said even picking up a
OL,16,Fknife with an intent to "prod" his
OL,17,Fdaughter was unlawful.
