OL,3,CParents of girl who died in kitchen
OL,4,Cincident serving 'life sentences',
OL,5,Cjury told
OL,7,FMr McKone said: "This has gone beyond
OL,8,Fhorseplay and Mr Vickers could and
OL,9,Fshould have realised there was a risk
OL,10,Fin that small kitchen of causing
OL,11,Fserious injury with a knife."
OL,13,FVickers denies murder and manslaughter.
OL,15,FMr Justice Cotter sent the jury out to
OL,16,Fconsider their verdicts before they
OL,17,Fwere sent home to carry on
OL,18,Fdeliberations on Thursday morning.
